MIT License — Agents of Empires Art Assets

Copyright (c) 2026 Rabid Troll Studios LLC

This directory contains original game art for Agents of Empires. The art is
released under the MIT License and is intended to be maximally open — free for
anyone to use, including teachers using it in classrooms, with no restriction.
See the root LICENSE file for how this fits into the repository's overall
license map.

Provenance note: the art in this directory is generated with self-hosted,
open-source AI image models (e.g. Stable Diffusion / SDXL, FLUX.1 Schnell) run
locally, and/or hand-authored. It contains no third-party proprietary asset-
store content. See docs/art-generation.md for the generation pipeline and each
unit's manifest under art/units/ for its reproducibility metadata.

